HEADWORD: Tappoon
<hw>Tap*poon"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp.
<ets>tamp⟦oacute⟧n</ets> a stopper.]</ety> <fld>(Irrigation)</fld>
